terational narcotics traffic include: the Senate Foreign Relations Committee (and its Subcommittee on Terrorism, Narcotics, and
International Operations), the House Foreign Affairs Committee (and its Task Force on International Narcotics Control), the Armed Services Committees, the House Ways and Means Committee, the Appropriations Committees, the Banking Committees, the Government Operations Committees, the Judiciary Committees, the Merchant Marine and Fisheries Committees, and the Agriculture Committees.
